dct_description_sm: Shows alluvium, younger and older sedimentary rocks, lavas and granitic rocks.
"The rock distribution has been compiled from published and unpublished data of the U.S. Geological Survey and from the Geologic map of California issued by the State Mining Bureau in 1891."
From U.S. Geological Survey Water-Supply Paper 338, pl. 2.
